title: Contraband Sports 13019 Sport Face Cover / Sport Mask - Nylon/Spandex Washable & Breathable - 6 Colors - (SOLD AS A SET)
description: Pull On closure ELASTIC TRIM - Designed to allow the mask to stretch for a comfortable fit on the ears. The fabric itself will also stretch to allow you to create a customized fit. SOLD AS A SET - Set 3 is sold as a 6pc set of masks, all other variations contain 4 masks. See product photos for confirmation of which each set includes. NYLON SPANDEX - A better option for sports where breathability is required such as weight lifting, cycling, rowing, jogging, running and other sports. MACHINE WASHABLE - Easy to wash with NO dye bleeding. We recommend hand washing to prevent damage but if you do prefer to machine wash, we suggest using a nylon mesh bag to protect the masks. Air dry only with no heat. NO HASSLE RETURNS and WARRANTY - There is a full purchase price refund within 30 days of your purchase if you are not happy for any reason. After 30 days, there is a 1yr full replacement warranty on these gloves for any manufacturing defect.
